adrFormatAddress: 520 8th Ave, New York, NY 10018, USA

originalText.text: I booked a beginner twerk class for my friend's birthday party a couple weeks prior to the day and fully paid and received confirmation. THE DAY OF THE PARTY I was told that they COULD NOT hold our class at the time we had booked. We already had babysitters, dinner reservations, and everyone coordinated to come at 7pm. When I agreed to move it to 8pm for a discount, they canceled on me and never responded again. AND THEY TOOK MY MONEY! I would never, never, never book here again and do not recommend it if you are relying on booking for an event or special occasion.
